The United Nations has proposed a plan in Canc<0xC3><0xBA>n to restore home lighting, trade and industrial space in 100 countries to achieve a greenhouse effect (GHG) limit, which corresponds to almost one-third of the additional limit that needs to be achieved to stabilize the planet’s climate from 2020 to now.
